data.description: Come home to one of Va Beach's premiere neighborhoods, Courthouse Estates.  This home located in Wythe Village features Open Great Room and Kitchen.  Granite counters, large pantry, Stainless appliances, Bay window, Breakfast area.  Enjoy relaxing around the fire pit in the quiet backyard. Plenty of storage in the large two car garage.  Large primary bedroom with large bathroom. Separate garden tub/shower. Upgraded vinyl plank flooring. Custom shed, pergola covered patio. Courthouse Estates close to wonderful restaurants, shopping, medical, beaches and schools. Call today for showing.
